snippet.title: Girls' Frontline
snippet.description:
Greetings, Commander! Girls' Frontline is a mobile Simulation and Collection game developed by Mica-Team（Sunborn Co., Ltd. Shanghai）. It is an era of chaos and darkness for the world, and you are gonna play the role of a commander working under a private military contractor to restore the orders by commanding troops of T-Dolls. As the players progresse through the game, they will gradually get closer to exposing the far-reaching conspiracy that permeates the world.

Looking for more information？
Official Site⇒ http://gf.sunborngame.com/
Official Facebook⇒ https://www.facebook.com/girlsfrontline/
Official Twitter⇒ https://twitter.com/GirlsFrontlineE
